          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-center">Budget-Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-center">One-time purchase eliminates ongoing subscription costs for schools and students</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
